{"tid":1851401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後見到大陸人賣口罩唔好拍片屌，會失民意","createTime":"2020-01-30T04:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T05:08:48.000Z","uid":333890,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"56875ee562443f28d02ba7837b8e8009e43d77e1","tid":1851401,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEWppCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEWppCQ.jpg&h=14cebe39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/weNsnpB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FweNsnpB.jpg&h=2367a68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ueOnVKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FueOnVKF.jpg&h=6fc435bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲拍片屌？佢依家搞到香港更快爆發生化災難，仲要因為咁賺哂啲乜都唔識嘅傻佬錢，正仆街人血病毒毒瘤典範<br />\n再唔做嘢就真係失民意</span></span><br />\n<br />\nLevel 1: 唔理佢，懦夫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Level 10: 屌爆佢，擺佢上網公審，都算係叫街坊小心啲（？）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Level 60: 搶佢啲貨扔咗佢，一勞永逸以免為禍人間</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Level 100: 直接一腳踢落佢塊支那面度，記得蒙面反跟蹤仲有事後洗鞋以免感染</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人自救，踢走支那畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9b2e90df697bfef059ee05e16647792c6f0d38","tid":1851401,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"睇住班支那廢老，笑左出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔識上網又資訊唔流通，食二手貨食假貨就係呢班，一話有就出去成班交叉感染。仲要肺炎死得多廢老，今次將人口大換血<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e341442f32b9cee82760258